
You can draw route through this code :
DrawRouteMaps.getInstance(getActivity())
                                    .draw(SOURCE_LATLNG,
                                          DESTINATION_LATLNG,
                                            map,
                                            "&key=YOUR_API_KEY"));
                                            
SOURCE_LATLNG -> new LatLng(SOURCE_LATITUDE, SOURCE_LONGITUDE)                                 
DESTINATION_LATLNG -> new LatLng(DESTINATION_LATITUDE, DESTINATION_LONGITUDE)
